</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-author-date" -->
<div class="forum-post-template-post">
<p>Thank you all, happy to join the conversation. The looking has really put an end to the fear of life, so simple I haven't really been able to talk about it, but thank God John talks and I really want to support this community. Maureen, Montreal</p>
</div><!-- class="forum-post-template-post" -->
